    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i don't even know who i am anymore. everything i worked for, the reputation, the respect... it's just gone. like i died and i'm just walking around as a ghost of who i used to be. i look in the mirror and i don't recognize the person staring back. there's nothing left.",
